description: This file defines a mock class SecureStorageServiceMock for unit testing gRPC service implementations related to secure storage. It includes mock methods for gRPC service methods such as GetValue, UpdateValue, DeleteValue, DeleteAllValues, and SeedValue, based on the SecureStorageService gRPC service.
